 Garib Newaz, director of the International Institute of the Juche Idea, Rosanita Campos, secretary of the October 8 Revolutionary Movement of Brazil, Rarissa Levy Cheva, managing director of Rio-Press in Krasnoyarsk of Russia, Manju Ratna Sakya, chairman of the Nepal Journalist Association, and other figures recalled that the President laid down a unique line of nation-building and wisely led the struggle to implement it. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
