 It pointed out that Kim Jong Il has glorified the DPRK as Kim Il Sung's Korea in name and reality and strengthened and developed the DPRK government as a powerful political weapon for realizing the idea and cause of the President by defending and steadily inheriting and developing the President's Juche-oriented line of building the people's power and his exploits. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
