 We will carry on the dynamic struggle to implement the June 15 joint declaration and the October 4 declaration under the uplifted banner of "By our nation itself" and resolutely foil the evermore undisguised moves of the separatist forces at home and abroad against the reunification and for a war of aggression against the DPRK, the letter said.

