Board of Directors of IIJI Meets
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, September 8 (KCNA) -- The 18th meeting of the Board of Directors of the International Institute of the Juche Idea (IIJI) was held in Pyongyang on Sept. 8. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
