&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, September 8 (KCNA) -- The Committee for Independent Reunification of the Democratic Labor Party in south Korea made public a statement on Sept. 4 in denunciation of the puppet military authorities' moves to expand the Mugon-ri training ground. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
