 The statement said that the DPRK could firmly defend the socialist cause despite the severe circumstances as it is guided by the Juche idea and the Songun idea founded by President Kim Il Sung and it has been turned into a powerful socialist fortress, which fully guarantees the sovereignty of the country and happiness of the people, under the Songun politics pursued by General Secretary Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The DPRK is absolutely supported and trusted by all the people as it has invariably enforced such social policies as free medical care and free educational systems, which can hardly be expected in other countries, even under the difficult situation caused by the persistent obstructive moves of the imperialists, it stressed. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It expressed belief that the socialist cause of the DPRK, a great encouragement to the world progressive people, would surely win under the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il.

DPRK's Birthday Observed in Different Countries
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, September 9 (KCNA) -- Round-table talks were held in Iran, a lecture was given in Ethiopia and a film show held in Thailand on Sept. 3 on the occasion of the 60th anniversary of the foundation of the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chairman of the Committee for International Relations of the Iran Parties House said at the round-table talks that the DPRK has grown strong amidst the confrontation with the U.S. from the very day of its foundation. The DPRK did not collapse unlike other countries but has made a dynamic advance despite the ceaseless U.S. moves to stifle it because President Kim Il Sung, father of the nation-building, built the DPRK into a popular masses-centered state, he added. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chairman of the Ethiopian Youth Study Group of the Juche Idea noted in the lecture that the DPRK is called "Kim Il Sung's Korea" because exploits Kim Il Sung performed by founding and developing the DPRK are so great and immortal. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He stressed that thanks to the leadership of Kim Jong Il the DPRK would always shine along with the august name of Kim Il Sung. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The manager of a Thai company said after watching a Korean film showing the appearance of the army and people single-mindedly united around the leader that even the U.S. styling itself the world's "only superpower" dares not provoke the DPRK thanks to the Songun politics of Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 An opening ceremony of a Korean book, photo and handcraft exhibition was held in Warsaw on Sept. 1 on the occasion of the 60th birthday of the DPRK and the 60th anniversary of the opening of diplomatic relations between the DPRK and Poland. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On display there were works of Kim Il Sung and Kim Jong Il and photos showing their immortal exploits, books and photos dealing with Songun Korea and handicrafts representing the resourcefulness and skills of the Koreans.

Mexican Party Leader Praises Glorious History of DPRK
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, September 9 (KCNA) -- Jesus Antonio Carlos Hernandez, general secretary of the Central Committee of the People's Socialist Party of Mexico, issued a statement on September 2 on the occasion of the 60th birthday of the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The statement said that the founding and development of the DPRK was the brilliant realization of the strategy and tactics shaped and matured by President Kim Il Sung, the great leader of the Korean people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Recalling that the revolutionary struggle of the Korean people has made a dynamic advance under the banner of the Juche idea and the Songun idea, he noted that the DPRK has achieved world-startling successes in various fields including the launch of satellite "Kwangmyongsong 1." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The statement said that in the DPRK the welfare of the people has been steadily promoted, they are free from the burden of taxation and free medical care and free education have been substantially enforced and culture and arts have effloresced. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It expressed belief that the cause of national reunification would be achieved and the DPRK would fling open the gate of a great prosperous powerful nation in 2012 marking the centenary of birth of the President under the wise leadership of Kim Jong Il, the great leader of the Korean people.

