 Miroslav Stepan, general secretary of the above-said committee, in his speech made at the meeting said that the DPRK has achieved big successes in the struggle to defend socialism and strengthen and develop it under the wise leadership of President Kim Il Sung and General Secretary Kim Jong Il over the last six decades. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
