 Present there on invitation were representatives of different organizations of Hiroshima Prefecture waging the friendship and solidarity movement with the DPRK and citizens of all strata and officials of the Hiroshima Prefectural Headquarters of the General Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongryon). &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
